				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$65^\circ$$\end{document}C core temperatures on standard AWS EC2 instances (m5.2xlarge). These metrics demonstrate that our optimizations successfully break the traditional throughput-CPU utilization tradeoff in permissioned blockchains. Figure 8 illustrates the CPU usage comparison.Fig. 9
