Sybil attackMalicious actors create fake identities to subvert node majorityOur permissioned PBFT network requires hardware-secured node attestation with multi-factor cryptographic proofs. Each node must pass government-issued TLS client certificates and biometric verification before participating in consensus, enforced through an on-chain registry smart contract with revocation capabilities
